value.0: Nova. An initiative started to end the constant warring in the galaxy. Led by the Jedi, funded by Senators all over the galaxy, the Nova Initiative is here to save the day. At least, it means to.
This appears to be the uniform of a Czerka Corporation employee.

Welcome to Star Wars: Legends of the Old Republic!

We're extremely happy you've stopped in to try our server out. We'll keep this brief so you can get in-game as quickly as possible.

Here are a few things you should know:

1.) Press 'C' or open your character sheet to access important options.

2.) You can purchase some starting items from the vendor in the northern part of this area.

3.) You can customize your character appearance from the 'Appearance' button in your character sheet.

4.) We log ALL chat messages, including tells, to our database for auditing purposes. By continuing to play here you agree to allow your conversations to be stored.


If you need more information about our unique gameplay please visit our website at https://www.starwarsnwn.com/

If you need further help please visit our Discord channel: https://discord.gg/MyQAM6m


May the Force be with you!
